          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/15984109-cloaked-in-red">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24421069-lorena?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>, 
