  <span id="freeText17453533102311601905" style="display:none">This is an anthology of Little Red Riding Hood retellings. There are eight different stories, some better than others. Velde also uses inspiration from other children's stories, like Three Little Pigs and Hansel and Gretel. These are all silly, funny stories, kind of making fun of how ridiculous the Little Red Riding Hood is. It was nothing special and not worth the time reading.</span>
