<span id="freeTextContainer17580200424874875487">Little Red Riding Hood is one of the silliest fairy tales out there- seriously the girl (who doesn&apos;t even have a name!) has no common sense. So these short stories are rather thin being based off the original source material. The best of the bunch was &quot;Deems the Wood Gatherer&quot; who bumbled around the enchanted woods making things worse for the three little pigs, LRRH, the Gingerbread Man &amp; Hansel and Gretel. A very fast read, so no harm done. </span>
