<div id="review_269283335" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/269283335" />
    <a title="Megan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5372197-megan"><img alt="Megan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1525475166p2/5372197.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/269283335?book_show_action=true">Feb 26, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Megan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Megan" href="/user/show/5372197-megan">Megan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5372197-megan?shelf=read-in-2019">read-in-2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5372197-megan?shelf=february-2019">february-2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5372197-megan?shelf=borrow-or-need-to-buy">borrow-or-need-to-buy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5372197-megan?shelf=gimme-a-v-yabrc-february-2019">gimme-a-v-yabrc-february-2019</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer269283335" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10957115993675654838">This is a collection of eight Little Red Riding Hood retellings/reimaginings. Some I thought had good ideas, but since the book is so short the stories weren&apos;t very fleshed out and kind of felt flat. None of the stories stood out as great, but the one (Little Red Riding Hood&apos;s Family) was perhaps the most bizarre. This was easy to read, since it wasn&apos;t that long, but it&apos;s not a book I&apos;d recommend.</span>
  <span id="freeText10957115993675654838" style="display:none">This is a collection of eight Little Red Riding Hood retellings/reimaginings. Some I thought had good ideas, but since the book is so short the stories weren't very fleshed out and kind of felt flat. None of the stories stood out as great, but the one (Little Red Riding Hood's Family) was perhaps the most bizarre. This was easy to read, since it wasn't that long, but it's not a book I'd recommend.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10957115993675654838" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


