<div id="review_2276143280" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2276143280" />
    <a title="Mandy" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3040481-mandy"><img alt="Mandy" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442810919p2/3040481.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2276143280?book_show_action=true">Mar 04, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mandy" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mandy" href="/user/show/3040481-mandy">Mandy</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/15984109-cloaked-in-red">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2276143280" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1298649944881048395">What a charming collection of short shorts exploring different aspects and what-ifs of the Little Red Riding Hood tale! <br/>My faves: Granny and the Wolf, for Granny’s and the wolf’s smarts and Deems the Wood Gatherer for the hilarious way he unintentionally interferes with other fairy tale stories. <br/><br/>A quick must-read for any lover of childhood fairy tales.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

